data.description:
Here's your opportunity to own a home located in the desirable Westgate Community! This three bedroom, two and a half bath home holds all entertaining space on the first floor and all bedrooms on the second. The living room includes vaulted ceiling and fireplace. Open kitchen with abundance of cabinetry and prep space. A laundry room and half bath are located just before the garage door. The privacy fenced rear yard with patio is ready to transform into your outdoor oasis.
New HVAC in 2022. New Roof in 2022. New Stainless steel appliances in 2023. New garage door to be installed prior to closing! The community features beach volleyball court, playground, clubhouse and pool. All within 20 minutes of Ft. Liberty!
